  list of favorites for easy shopping every time;
* enjoy free standard shipping for nonprescription products (a limited time
  offer);
* enter your credit card information just once; and
* view your online order and account status.

Merck-Medco's world-class mail service pharmacies will continue to dispense
and ship your prescriptions, and CVS/pharmacy will ship your nonprescription
order.

And while you're visiting merckmedco.com, be sure to check out our other 
areas:
* My Prescriptions, to refill and renew existing Merck-Medco mail service
  prescriptions, check prescription status and review prescription history;
* My Benefits, where you can manage your Merck-Medco pharmacy benefit;
* My Health, to discover a world of health information; and
* My Page, to find special announcements developed with you in mind.

Your merckmedco.com registration is the key to a world of health and
information resources - and now one-stop shopping for nonprescription
drugstore products - right at your fingertips.


